com.ojcoleman.europa.configurable

Annotation Type Parameter


  • @Documented
@Target(value=FIELD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Parameter

    For fields in sub-classes of ConfigurableBase, this annotation indicates that the field is user configurable, e.g. via a JSON configuration file. See ConfigurableBase for more information.

    Author:
    O. J. Coleman
    See Also:
    Configurable, Prototype, Component

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.String description
      Description for the sub-component.

      A default value for the parameter.

      boolean optional
      Whether the parameter is optional.
